replies.body:
Thats the point of the ARURF...We cannot have old URF back in my opinion ..Everyone would be picking only OP champions such as Katarina, Zed, yas, Talon Karthus..+ etc so on...If you didn't want a certain champion you could of just dodged and waited out the 5:00min timer .. your friends would understand.
And if they're ruining your fun, just use the special button "Mute" it solves it much easier than Trash talking one of your teammates..And don't do that in all chat report them on your own, all chatting to make other people be on your side is bad. :/ (Cause they're probably going to think you're doing the Chaos, and Syndra, and Ashe are not doing anything wrong) so just for the word for advice. 

Another thing, only Report in URF if you got an AFK....As you said it's suppose to be fun..So like mm.{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
